_:e93cd5477ecf0ed7ba3dd763924ed7e0 a <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E52_Time-span> ;
	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> "Barbara was the beautiful daughter of the pagan Dioscorus. He locked his daughter up in a tower. \n                  She converted to Christianity, and her father beat her and handed her over to be martyred. Her example inspired another Christian woman, Juliana, to come to her aid. \n                  Both women were martyred." .
